      "cookedHtml": "<p>We’ve been busy over the last few weeks making updates and improvements to the API and apps. Check out what’s changed below!</p>\n<h1><a name=\"p-172618-api-2024-04httpsdevelopermondaycomapi-referencedocsrelease-notes2024-04-1\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-172618-api-2024-04httpsdevelopermondaycomapi-referencedocsrelease-notes2024-04-1\"></a>API (<a href=\"https://developer.monday.com/api-reference/docs/release-notes#2024-04\"><code>2024-04</code></a>)</h1>\n<h2><a name=\"p-172618-breaking-changes-2\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-172618-breaking-changes-2\"></a>Breaking changes</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>New <a href=\"https://developer.monday.com/api-reference/changelog/new-kind-field-enum-values-on-version-and-versions-queries\"><code>kind</code></a> field enum values</li>\n</ul>\n<h2><a name=\"p-172618-non-breaking-changes-3\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-172618-non-breaking-changes-3\"></a>Non-breaking changes</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>New <a href=\"https://developer.monday.com/api-reference/changelog/new-is_default_workspace-field\"><code>is_default_workspace</code></a> field</li>\n<li>New <a href=\"https://developer.monday.com/api-reference/changelog/new-create_item-mutation-arguments\"><code>create_item</code></a> mutation arguments</li>\n<li>New field and argument on <a href=\"https://developer.monday.com/api-reference/changelog/new-field-and-argument-on-app_installs-queries\"><code>app_installs</code></a> object</li>\n<li>New <a href=\"https://developer.monday.com/api-reference/changelog/new-field-on-version-and-versions-queries\"><code>display_name</code></a> field on <code>version</code> and <code>versions</code> objects</li>\n</ul>\n<h1><a name=\"p-172618-apps-4\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-172618-apps-4\"></a>Apps</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>New <a href=\"https://community.monday.com/t/introducing-an-impactful-feature-to-boost-app-installations/76391\">demo experience</a> for marketplace apps</li>\n<li>New security and compliance <a href=\"https://developer.monday.com/apps/changelog/new-security-and-compliance-questionnaire\">questionnaire</a></li>\n</ul>"
